.TH "snd_hda_codec_prepare" 9 "snd_hda_codec_prepare" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hda_codec_prepare \- Prepare a stream
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hda_codec_prepare
.BI "(struct hda_codec *codec "  ","
.BI "struct hda_pcm_stream *hinfo "  ","
.BI "unsigned int stream "  ","
.BI "unsigned int format "  ","
.BI "struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "codec" 12
the HDA codec
.IP "hinfo" 12
PCM information
.IP "stream" 12
stream tag to assign
.IP "format" 12
format id to assign
.IP "substream" 12
PCM substream to assign
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Calls the prepare callback set by the codec with the given arguments.
Clean up the inactive streams when successful.
